---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 337
  - Title: Artha-sâstra
    Location: I 3
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=Concerning Right Vocation
    or ‘Dharma'
  - 679
---
Vocation leads to heaven and eternity; in case of a digression from
this norm, the world is brought to ruin by confusion.
